                  Yeah, the Bible is thousands of years old, even Jewish scholars can show parts where the Torah has been badly edited or changed.<br />
So, arguing over the exact actions of Abraham etc...is like arguing over Ceasar's words at some battle, which are only recorded second hand, by a multi-generation copy, done from numerous tongues etc. Useful, but almost assuredly, not accurate.<br />
<br />
Look, how many of you have seen an actual interview/person's exact words, and then seen the TV idiots absolutely bucher it with editing etc to deliberately twist it, or in their gross stupidity or desire to &quot;hit the lowest common moron&quot;, wreck what was actually meant?<br />
<br />
<i>So WTF is anyone taking the Bible word for literal word?!</i><br />
<br />
Faith != Religion, religion is the enemy of Man and God. What always happens, is that because we Humans are so fearful fo being &quot;left outside the group&quot;, if one sod says: &quot;<i>Your'e damned if you don't do it THIS way</i>!&quot; most folk will follow blindly, regardless of their own inner inclinations, because most folk lack the guts or the obstinacy to tell those a'holes to go F' off.<br />
<br />
Fear, IMHo is the root of all Evil, not greed. People rob because of fear of not having enough/thier share or fear driving them cuckoo; people kill due to fear (loss of power, threat to life, fear driving them cucko)...etc...<br />
<br />
<i>Thus, since people follow religion almost always out of FEAR, it is an inherently evil thing</i>. VERY few folk truly follow a religion (at least Christianity/Islam) only out of *love* or simple belief. Nearly always a major ocmponent is fear of social exlucison or damnation, when they are NOT evil people!<br />
-You only have to look at the early Christian church, and what Mohammed did after Medina, to see this.
                  
